quran[15]{c,v,t,f}:
  26,118,"Nítorí náà, ṣèdájọ́ tààrà láààrin èmi àti àwọn. Kí o sì la èmi àti àwọn tó wà pẹ̀lú mi nínú àwọn onígbàgbọ́ òdodo.”"
  26,119,"A la òun àti àwọn tó wà pẹ̀lú rẹ̀ nínú ọkọ̀ ojú-omi tó kún kẹ́kẹ́."
  26,120,"Lẹ́yìn náà, A tẹ àwọn tó ṣẹ́kù rì sínú omi."
  27,91,"Ohun tí wọ́n pa mí ní àṣẹ rẹ̀ ni pé kí n̄g jọ́sìn fún Olúwa Ìlú yìí, Ẹni tí Ó ṣe é ní àyè ọ̀wọ̀. TiRẹ̀ sì ni gbogbo n̄ǹkan. Wọ́n sì pa mí ní àṣẹ pé kí èmi wà nínú àwọn mùsùlùmí."
  27,92,"Àti pé kí èmi máa ké al-Ƙur’ān. Nítorí náà, ẹnikẹ́ni tí ó bá mọ̀nà, ó mọ̀nà fún ẹ̀mí ara rẹ̀. Ẹnikẹ́ni tí ó bá sì ṣìnà, sọ pé: “Dájúdájú èmi wà nínú àwọn olùkìlọ̀.”"
  27,93,"Sọ pé: “Gbogbo ẹyìn ń jẹ́ ti Allāhu.” (Allāhu) yóò fi àwọn àmì Rẹ̀ hàn yín. Ẹ̀yin yó sì mọ̀ wọ́n. Olúwa rẹ kò sì gbàgbé ohun tí ẹ̀ ń ṣe níṣẹ́."
  28,64,"A sọ (fún wọn) pé: “Ẹ pe àwọn òrìṣà yín.” Wọ́n sì pè wọ́n, ṣùgbọ́n wọn kò dá wọn lóhùn. Wọ́n ti rí Iná. Tí ó bá jẹ́ pé dájúdájú wọ́n jẹ́ olùmọ̀nà ni (ìyà ìbá tí jẹ wọ́n.)"
  28,65,"(Rántí) ọjọ́ tí (Allāhu) yóò pè wọ́n, Ó sì máa sọ pé: “Kí ni ẹ fọ̀ ní èsì fún àwọn Òjíṣẹ́?”"
  28,66,"Èsì ọ̀rọ̀ yó sì fọ́jú pọ̀ mọ́ wọn lọ́wọ́ ní ọjọ́ yẹn; wọn kò sì níí bira wọn léèrè ìbéèrè.1 {1}",1:[Ẹ wo ìtọsẹ̀-ọ̀rọ̀ sūrah al-Mu’minūn;  23:101.]
  29,31,"Nígbà tí àwọn Òjíṣẹ́ Wa sì mú ìró ìdùnnú dé bá (Ànábì) ’Ibrọ̄hīm, wọ́n sọ pé: “Dájúdájú àwa máa pa àwọn ará ìlú yìí run. Dájúdájú àwọn ará ìlú náà jẹ́ alábòsí.”"
  29,32,"Ó sọ pé: “Dájúdájú (Ànábì) Lūt wà níbẹ̀! Wọ́n sọ pé: “Àwa nímọ̀ jùlọ nípa àwọn tó wà níbẹ̀. Dájúdájú àwa yóò la òun àti àwọn ará ilé rẹ̀ àfi ìyàwó rẹ̀ tí ó máa wà nínú àwọn tó máa ṣẹ́kù lẹ́yìn sínú ìparun.”"
  29,33,"Nígbà tí àwọn Òjíṣẹ́ Wa dé ọ̀dọ̀ (Ànábì) Lūt, ó banújẹ́ nítorí wọn. Agbára rẹ̀ kò sì ká ọ̀rọ̀ wọn mọ́. Wọ́n sì sọ fún un pé: “Má bẹ̀rù, má sì ṣe banújẹ́. Dájúdájú a máa la ìwọ àti àwọn ará ilé rẹ àfi ìyàwó rẹ tí ó máa wà nínú àwọn olùṣẹ́kù-lẹ́yìn sínú ìparun.”"
  30,10,"Lẹ́yìn náà, aburú jẹ́ àtubọ̀tán àwọn tó ṣaburú nítorí pé, wọ́n pe àwọn āyah Allāhu ní irọ́. Wọ́n sì ń fi ṣe yẹ̀yẹ́."
  30,11,"Allāhu ń pilẹ̀ ẹ̀dá dídá. Lẹ́yìn náà, O máa dá a padà (sípò alààyè). Lẹ́yìn náà, ọ̀dọ̀ Rẹ̀ ni wọn yóò da yín padà sí."
  30,12,"Ní ọjọ́ tí Àkókò náà máa ṣẹlẹ̀, àwọn ẹlẹ́ṣẹ̀ yó sọ̀rètí nù."